  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beyond The Limits</strong> is an open-world crime game set in a city where freedom comes with consequences. Explore the streets, steal vehicles, engage in combat, and complete missions across the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on action and exploration, delivering a direct experience in a dynamic urban environment. Move through the city, cause chaos, or complete objectives as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Current features include:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-world city to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vehicle stealing mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon-based combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable missions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planned updates:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded story mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New missions and challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional content and improvements</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beyond The Limits</strong> is an open-world crime game set in a city where freedom comes with consequences. Explore the streets, steal vehicles, engage in combat, and complete missions across the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on action and exploration, delivering a direct experience in a dynamic urban environment. Move through the city, cause chaos, or complete objectives as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Current features include:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-world city to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vehicle stealing mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon-based combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable missions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planned updates:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded story mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New missions and challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional content and improvements</p></li></ul>",
